data.name: groupBox1.Text
data.value: Ready to embark on a new career, but don’t have the time (or money) to spend four years getting a bachelor’s degree? A short-term job training program might be just the ticket for you to gain access to a rewarding career field.

data.name: groupBox2.Text
data.value: There are a surprising number of fields you can enter without completing long degree programs. Many offer salaries and job satisfaction similar to those that require four-year degrees. If you’re in the market for a job change, consider a short-term job training program in a growing occupation. You may find that you can qualify quickly for a rewarding new job.
